  "_index": "Zm",
  "title": "Scarlet & Violet",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "_id": "37XBzLKUiAWhWdtZutLso8hdH7x",
      "_index": "a0",
      "_type": "TextBlock",
      "text": [
        {
          "_type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "The Scarlet & Violet series of the Pokémon TCG takes players to the vast "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Paldea region",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": ", introducing the first Generation IX Pokémon and the powerful "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Pokémon ex",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": " mechanic. This era revitalized the game by bringing back the ex designation and introducing "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Tera Pokémon ex",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": ", featuring stunning crystalline artwork and unique strategic abilities, such as immunity to damage while on the Bench."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Visually, the series marked a historic shift for the international hobby. Most notably, the traditional yellow borders used since the game's inception were replaced with "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "sleek silver borders",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": " to match the Japanese card designs."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}